<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id6057a2e5-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58" identifier="/us/usc/t30/s1515"><num value="1515">§ 1515.</num><heading> Regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall promulgate regulations to carry out this subchapter no later than six months after <date date="1980-06-30">June 30, 1980</date>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id6057a2e6-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58">(<ref href="/us/pl/96/294/tVI/s615">Pub. L. 96–294, title VI, § 615</ref>, <date date="1980-06-30">June 30, 1980</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/94/764">94 Stat. 764</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
